      "title": "The smallest Moufang loop revisited",
      "abstract": "We derive presentations for Moufang loops oftype M2n(G, 2), defined by Chein, with G finite, two-generated. We then use G = 8 3 to visualize the smallest non-associative Moufang loop. MATH. SUBJECT CLASSIFICATION: Primary: 20N05, Secondary: 20F05 KEYWORDS: Moufang loop, presentations of loops, loops M2n(G, 2)."
